      <title>壳牌维持回购，削减债务，利润超出预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/shell-maintains-buyback-reduces-debt-as-profit-beats-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司公布第二季度收益超过预期，并确认再回购 35 亿美元股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/shell-maintains-buyback-reduces-debt-as-profit-beats-estimates</guid>
